<div type="addressee">
<ab>Graf <expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von Wertheim,
                            <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> des stifts zu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten
                        frewnde der von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir nehst <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> gesandt <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        sich ewr gnade zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweiset, denn daz ir von
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> geschefts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>pieten</expan>
                        lieszt. Nu sein uns sölich sache noch niht lieb und
                            <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir icht guts darczu
                                <expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz es
                            <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> und den von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> abgieng, des
                            <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir willig sein. Und wan sölich sache auf
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> best
                                <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan> wurde, so
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnade mit fleisz, ir wellet umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und von den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        reden <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> und <add>uns</add> bey disem botten
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan>, was
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darinn sein welle. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb und dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
